@startuml
title UC04 - View Match Details Sequence
actor Visitor
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Match API" as API
participant "Match Detail Service" as Svc
database "DB" as DB
Visitor -> UI : Open match details
UI -> API : GET /matches/{id}
API -> Svc : getDetails(id, viewer)
Svc -> DB : load match, criteria, stats, comments
DB --> Svc : detail data
Svc --> API : public/detail DTO
API --> UI : 200 OK / 404
UI --> Visitor : Display details or not found
@enduml
